WEBVTT

1
00:12:08.312 --> 00:12:10.479
<font color="#fecb00">Colonel. your dossier
says you speak French.</font>

2
00:12:10.480 --> 00:12:12.482
<font color="#fecb00">If this is true. clear your throat.</font>

3
00:12:14.735 --> 00:12:18.197
<font color="#fecb00">Excellent. Count to six. then drop.</font>

4
00:22:44.656 --> 00:22:45.657
<font color="#fecb00">Doctor Suzuki?</font>

5
00:22:47.826 --> 00:22:48.827
<font color="#fecb00">Pardon us.</font>

6
00:22:50.787 --> 00:22:51.787
<font color="#fecb00">Doctor Miura!</font>

7
00:22:52.748 --> 00:22:55.625
<font color="#fecb00">My apologies for not
anticipating your arrival.</font>

8
00:22:55.626 --> 00:22:57.043
<font color="#fecb00">Oh. my apologies as well.</font>

9
00:22:57.044 --> 00:22:58.961
<font color="#fecb00">The locals are too scared to bring</font>

10
00:22:58.962 --> 00:23:01.089
<font color="#fecb00">my mail or messages anymore.</font>

11
00:23:02.424 --> 00:23:04.384
<font color="#fecb00">Even my assistant ran away.</font>

12
00:23:09.348 --> 00:23:11.850
<font color="#fecb00">Welcome to Monster Island.</font>

13
00:26:34.469 --> 00:26:35.554
<font color="#fecb00">Why can't you trust him?</font>

14
00:34:03.252 --> 00:34:06.213
<font color="#fecb00">Miracles should be terrifying.</font>

15
00:34:06.839 --> 00:34:07.965
<font color="#fecb00">Don't you think?</font>
